# Files generated by `pnpm codegen`. Pinned here in lockstep with the
# `ignores` list in `eslint.config.mjs` — both lists must agree, since both
# tools fan out from `pnpm --filter @matchlayer/shared-types format/lint`.
#
# `openapi-typescript` and `openapi-zod-client` emit code patterns we don't
# control (long single-line type aliases, openapi-zod-client's HTML-entity
# encoding of OpenAPI description strings, idiosyncratic spacing). Running
# Prettier over them produces a noisy diff every codegen run, defeating the
# `openapi-drift` CI check (§9.1, §11.2) which expects byte-identical
# regeneration.
